Subject: Username doesnt show
Description: I deployed the EPP agent thru a Hexnode policy I created. The agent installed. On the server, his computer pops up, but his "Users" username doesn't pop up. Why is this happening? I've never seen this happen before
What_We_Know__c: The reported problem was caused by a licensing issue(one computer was registered multiple times and consumed all licenses). We have deleted the computer from Device Control and the newly deployed device start working.
Solution_Comment__c: The reported problem was caused by a licensing issue(one computer was registered multiple times and consumed all licenses). We have deleted the computer from Device Control and the newly deployed device start working.
